All Implemented Interfaces:
minijava.analysis.Analysis, minijava.node.Switch
public class SymTableVisitor
extends minijava.analysis.DepthFirstAdapter

This visitor class builds a symbol table as it traverses the tree. The table, an instance of ClassTable, can be returned via getTable().
